author: Disney
description:
I put a spell on you, and now you’re mine! D23 Inside Disney is getting into the Halloween spirit by the 10th anniversary of the fan-favorite “Hocus Pocus Villain Spelltacular” show at Mickey’s Not-So-Scary Halloween Party. Get ready to run amok (amok, amok, amok, amok!) throughout the spook-tacular celebration and get an sneak peek  behind the magic with the voice of Thackery Binx from Hocus Pocus, Jason Marsden!
